title: N64 ROMs - Full Set of 308 + 91 Japanese games (Complete set fro
description:
This torrent contains ROMs for all games released for Nintendo 64 as listed on the wiki at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Nintendo_64_games as well as many Japanese Super Famicom games.  Many are tested to work with Everdrive and emulators.

Files have been renamed to match exact title on wiki.  All have been converted to the newer .v64 format, and incorrect file extensions have been fixed.

Each file is .ZIP compressed and shared individually, but please seed as many of the files as you can.


Happy gaming!
